        <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl text-[#0f2e22] border-b border-[#0f2e22]/20 pb-2 mb-6">Phase I: Seed Portfolio &amp; Track Record</h2>
        <p class="font-sans text-base text-[#1a1a1a] leading-relaxed mb-4">
            Vanier Capital is currently operating in its Phase I Seed stage. We are purely self-funding acquisitions, stabilizing assets, and managing them in-house to build a documented track record of execution. This period is strictly designed to validate our underwriting models and prove our operational capabilities with our own capital before ever accepting outside investment.
        </p>
        <p class="font-sans text-base text-[#1a1a1a] leading-relaxed mb-4">
            Every acquisition, renovation, and lease-up is systematically documented with institutional-grade reporting. Our objective is to demonstrate repeatable, risk-adjusted performance before scaling capital under a formal placement structure.
        </p>

        <!-- Section 2: 24-Month Fund Launch -->
